4 — Slide 2: Engagements
(unchanged)

"Second layer — engagements. This is how any structured review runs on top of the platform. Not just audits — regulator inquiries, internal reviews, vendor assessments, incident reviews. Audit is one type."
"Four capabilities. Engagement starts with scope ready — day one is productive work, not preparation. The evidence package builds itself — reviewers review, never chase. Need more evidence mid-engagement? Already routed — same Power Automate pattern, no email chains. And years later, the engagement's view of the world is preserved permanently. When a regulator asks what you did for this control, on this app, in this period — the engagement record is the answer."

